Hi Ian,

The offset (ET) on passat wheels requires a 12mm spacer (and possibly  
longer studs) if you don't want to potentially mess up your bearings.

Any wheel that will fit a vanagon will also fit a baywindow... This  
page is an excellent resource for wheel options.

http://www.vanagon.com/info/tires/index.html


Happy Trails,

